org.dayatang.persistence.hibernate

Class UppercaseAndUnderscoreNamingStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dayatang.persistence.hibernate.UppercaseAndUnderscoreNamingStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hibernate.cfg.NamingStrategy

    public class UppercaseAndUnderscoreNamingStrategy
extends Object
implements org.hibernate.cfg.NamingStrategy
    Hibernate映射命名策略类。将表名和列名设定为大写字母形式，如果表名或列名由多个单词组成，单词之间用下划线隔开。
    Author:
    yyang (gdyangyu@gmail.com)
